# Force a textual diff for TypeScript sources. Historically tree.ts embedded
# control-char separators in its path-key tokens (a U+0000 null sentinel and a
# U+0001 key separator); they are now written as JS unicode escapes so the
# source is plain text. The `diff` attribute also keeps the *transition* diff
# reviewable: the pre-image blob still contains the raw U+0000, which would
# otherwise make Git render this very change as "Binary file". No eol/text
# normalization is applied.
*.ts diff
